name: DIVERSION | Lufthansa 747-430 [D-ABVU] Takeoff from Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Look at that condensation! Here we have an 18-year old Lufthansa 747-400 departing Calgary International Airport after a medical diversion en route from Frankfurt to Seattle as LH490. Sure was a nice treat to see this beauty, and with some amazing condensation as well, you don't see that very often in Calgary. Hopefully the passenger makes a speedy recovery. Enjoy this special catch.

Thanks for watching!
